Cool jobs: Sun, sand and sea in the office 30 April 2014 Last updated at 02:55 BST
Sun, sand and sea, that's the typical holiday for tired professionals looking to escape the office. But for one man, that's where he gets to work day in and day out. Could being the owner and manager of an Indonesian beach resort be one of Asia's Cool Jobs? The BBC's Alice Budisatrijo considers an island career..
